<h2>Customer Details </h2>
<p> This page displays all of the customer's contact, billing, shipping and login data. You can easily modify or update a customer's information and save it by clicking the Update button. You can also delete the customer if there are no orders associated with the customer. If there are orders associated with the customer the delete button will not be available.</p>
<p>The data shown here is captured on the Order Form when a customer places an order. The shipping data always reflects the shipping address given on the most recent order. </p>
<h3>Order History</h3>
<p>A complete order history is also displayed with links to the Orders details page to check on the status and details of an order. </p>
